Source People often don&rsquo;t know what frame they want for the family portrait, so they go to the shop and the assistant will put up various different frames against the picture so you can see what it looks like. Then people are able to voice their preferences like &ldquo;not this one, but similar, I want a lighter wood frame&rdquo;
